---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 141
By: Abu Sa'id ibn Abi TKhayr
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Detachment From Place and
    Conditions
  - Union-Identity=Holiness-Universal Man=Attributes of Holiness
---
The true saint goes in and out amongst the people and eats and sleeps with
them and buys and sells in the market and marries and takes part in social
intercourse, and never forgets God for a single moment.
